This repository contains code adapted from the following upstream project:

- Project: myl7/fss
- Repository: https://github.com/myl7/fss
- License: Apache License 2.0

Adapted components include the DPF CPU algorithm structure, utility helpers,
and the software AES-128 MMO PRG approach. The implementation in this
repository removes CUDA and OpenMP dependencies, replaces CUDA-specific data
types with standard C++ equivalents, and exposes a small C ABI for backend
integration.
